4 A BILL
5 TO BE ENTITLED
6 AN ACT
7
8
9 Relating to Montgomery County; to amend Section
10 45-51-84, Code of Alabama 1975, to further provide for the
11 compensation of the judge of probate.
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
13 Section 1. Section 45-51-84, Code of Alabama 1975, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 "§45-51-84
16 (a) The per annum compensation shall be eighty-eight
17 thousand dollars ($88,000) for the judge of probate effective
18 October 1, 1996.
19 (b) The compensation amount in subsection (a) shall be
20 paid out of the general fund of the Montgomery County
21 Commission in the same manner as other county employees are
22 paid.
23 (c) Subsequent to October 1, 1996, the compensation
24 amount in subsection (a) shall be increased by the same
25 percentage as the across-the-board percentage increase
26 received by full-time county employees at the same time as the
27 increase is received by the county employees, except that the
28 amount shall not be increased by more than three thousand
Page 1

amount shall not be increased by more than three thousand
