29 dollars ($3,000) in any fiscal year.
30 (d) Beginning October 1, 2026, the individual serving
31 as judge of probate on June 1, 2025, in lieu of any other
32 salary, shall receive an annual salary of one hundred
33 fifty-three thousand seven hundred twenty-five dollars
34 ($153,725) per year."
35 Section 2. This act shall become effective on June 1,
36 2026.
